1. Screenshot
   option + shift + 3 : to get a full screenshot
   option + shift + 4 : to get an area screenshot
2. Go up / Go down folder level
   command + up
   command + down (it can also open a file)
3. Get a Folder Path
   right click + option, then you can see an option "Copy something as FilePath"
4. Delete a file
   command + delete
5. Go to desktop
   command + F3
6. Close a window
   command + w
